				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-M%E1%BA%ADt/Cao-d%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%91%C3%A0i-K%C3%BD-Vi%E1%BB%87t-trung-ch%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-gCZu3ihGAmC2ewleau-d9Q">Cao dương đài - Ký Việt trung chư hữu - 高陽臺－寄越中諸友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-M%E1%BA%ADt/author-mzdbOPTBpV_wlws25Bzhyw">Chu Mật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/D%E1%BA%A1-quy-chu-trung-t%C3%A1c/poem-icABAAX04oi6NUAriAxA0A">Dạ quy chu trung tác - 夜歸舟中作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-h_HbFCmxWKkwxboqzaEfNA">Trần Nguyên Đán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%93-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Nguy%C3%AAn/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hy-Chi-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-Th%E1%BB%B1-t%E1%BB%A5c-thi%E1%BA%BFp/poem-Z-LKQJm1MvGnKlT55az1Fw">Đề Vương Hy Chi Phụng Thự tục thiếp - 題王羲之鳳墅續帖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%93-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-vNqjO3qn_lddcLSXVQdpGA">Bồ Đạo Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%C3%BAc-chu-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-G-aISXTO-rSkSnuTGXCoTw">Phúc chu kỳ 2 - 覆舟其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Minh-T%C3%B4ng/T%E1%BA%B7ng-b%E1%BA%AFc-s%E1%BB%A9-T%C3%A1t-Ch%E1%BB%89-Ngo%C3%A3-V%C4%83n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-EV3uobGl4ss7UWKLSD_g8Q">Tặng bắc sứ Tát Chỉ Ngoã, Văn Tử Phương - 贈北使撒只瓦，文子方</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Minh-T%C3%B4ng/author-4trx3YJ-cefKhX0g_XM7Sw">Trần Minh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-djGByRNyyXxtcykD8j_JTA">Thu dạ kỳ 2 - 秋夜其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-kinh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-Gzw1Tbyjb-IhRRXZrgX8KA">Thu kinh kỳ 1 - 收京其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-N%C3%A3i/T%E1%BB%91ng-Di%E1%BB%85n-Lu%C3%A2n-quy-l%C3%BD/poem-v3VjI5V9GfYhffYH7xMmmA">Tống Diễn Luân quy lý - 送演綸歸里</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-N%C3%A3i/author-Fd7oZerPVEVOXx_JIj1fmg">Diêu Nãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%E1%BA%A5t-huynh-ph%C3%B3-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%A2u-so%C3%A1i-m%E1%BA%A1c/poem-3zymIXZEHMiSBXKw9ewVOA">Tống thất huynh phó Dương Châu soái mạc - 送七兄赴揚州帥幕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Vi%C3%AAm-V%C5%A9/V%C5%A9-trung-ch%C3%AD-Hoa-h%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%BAc-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-S%C6%A1n-S%E1%BB%AD-gia/poem-R8tliClvgcCSP0mGl-QL7g">Vũ trung chí Hoa hạ túc Vương Sơn Sử gia - 雨中至華下宿王山史家</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Vi%C3%AAm-V%C5%A9/author-py5Vb_484Rgr_jQ_nkfQjw">Cố Viêm Vũ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
